parameters.name: DatasetName
parameters.description: The name of an existing dataset to associate this project with.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: A unique name for the new project. Valid characters are alphanumeric (A-Z, a-z, 0-9), hyphen (-), period (.), and space.

parameters.name: RecipeName
parameters.description: The name of an existing recipe to associate with the project.

parameters.name: Sample
parameters.description: Represents the sample size and sampling type for DataBrew to use for interactive data analysis. Size (integer) --- The number of rows in the sample. The way in which DataBrew obtains rows from a dataset.

nested_params.name: Size
nested_params.description: The number of rows in the sample.

nested_params.name: Type
nested_params.description: The way in which DataBrew obtains rows from a dataset.

parameters.name: RoleArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Identity and Access Management (IAM) role to be assumed for this request.

parameters.name: Tags
parameters.description: Metadata tags to apply to this project. (string) --- (string) ---
